{"tid":1640169,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國前國務卿希拉莉: 每個美國人都有挺港權利！","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:50:07.000Z","uid":296083,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dec35ba736798e1606591ca12aff270caa056073","tid":1640169,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2940950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2940950&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ5S9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=dc1e1a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2940950&h=e5933c31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2940950</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國職籃NBA休士頓火箭隊總經理莫雷「挺自由、撐香港」的言論讓萬千中國人心碎，更發起了一連串民族主義式的反NBA活動，體育事件上升成價值觀的論戰，美國前國務卿希拉蕊也跳入戰局，昨日在推特上發文，稱每個美國人都有挺香港的權利。<br />\n<br />\n希拉蕊在推特表示，「每個美國人都有權利發聲，表達自己對於香港民主與人權的支持，句點」（Every American has the right to voice their support for democracy and human rights for Hong Kong. Full stop.）這番話引起各國網友熱烈討論，有中國網民到希拉蕊的推特嗆聲「每個中國人都有權不觀看NBA，不使用美國產品。」香港網友則對於希拉蕊的發聲紛紛表達感謝。<br />\n對於中國網民壓迫、官媒批判甚至中國官方停止轉播NBA所有季前賽，NBA總裁席爾瓦8日在東京賽前記者會中表示，「毫無疑問，莫雷的發言導致龐大的經濟損失和嚴重後果，但我仍支持莫雷擁有言論自由，他有發表不同政治觀點的權利」。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔 做野啦 快點上FB回POST多謝 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線比本土抗爭更重要</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c9d72cc259a5fd43c3e028fc4a1d0430bfa51255","tid":1640169,"uid":238451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"希拉莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fb17131fb55d17e6d5b08ece8ac2a129b5fab7","tid":1640169,"uid":288221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:11:02.000Z","msg":"美國開始有